tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Pharmacies (
    pharmacy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    pharmacy_name VARCHAR(255),
    location VARCHAR(255),
    medication_inventory JSONB,
    medication_dispensing_logs JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE Dispensing (dispense_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
                  pharmacy_id INT,
                  patient_id INT,
                  medication_id INT,
                  dispense_date DATE,
                  quantity INT
);
